""""""""""Aesthetics
hi Hint font: bold 11px "Consolas", monospace !important; margin: -.2ex; padding: 0 0 0 0px; outline: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .5); background: rgba(255, 248, 231, .9); color: black; text-transform:uppercase;

""""""""""Fix hinttags so it finds more elements
:set hinttags+=a

""""""""""Bindings
"Scrolling
:map -builtin j 5j
:map -builtin k 5k
:map <A-j> <C-d>
:map <A-k> <C-u>

:map <S-J> :tabprev<CR>
:map <S-K> :tabnext<CR>

"Copying stuff. We lose the ability to stop the page from loading... but don't think I appreciate insert/caret/textarea mode sufficiently anyways
:map <C-c> <C-v><C-c>

:vmap <C-Tab> <C-v><C-Tab>
:vmap <C-S-Tab> <C-v><C-S-Tab>

"Insert mode hacks... not sure what the better hotkeys would be
:imap -builtin <C-a> <C-v><C-a>
:imap -builtin <C-v> <C-v><C-v>
:imap -builtin <C-z> <C-v><C-z>

"private window
:map <C-S-n> :private<Space>winopen<CR>

"Add dictionary to alt-shift-d
:map <A-S-d> :open http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/


""""""""""Quickmarks
:qmark o www.outlook.com/owa/microsoft.com
:qmark g www.gmail.com
:qmark s www.stackoverflow.com
:qmark w www.weather.com/weather/today/Redmond+WA+98052:4:US


